def get_instance_pci_devs(inst):
    """Get the devices assigned to the instances."""
    if isinstance(inst, objects.Instance):
        return inst.pci_devices
    else:
        ctxt = context.get_admin_context()
        return objects.PciDeviceList.get_by_instance_uuid(
            ctxt, inst['uuid'])

In the above code, the else part may not be used by the normal code flow. Removing it may break some of the unit tests. Thus fix is also needed in the unit test code that is using it.

